OOC: Airly, is that a 3d image of the Infecticon base? Because if it is... 
thats not possible. The bases design is only known to those on the infecticon 
side. Not to mention what it looks like fully. None of Darkfates Predacons 
have been able to see more then a single building. Not even Alecto because 
the sunlight doesnt reach the bottom. Its pitch black down there. So im 
hoping that 3d image is not of the base because that is rather impossible 
seeing as how none of the factions on the planet have no data on it.

--part1_c1.11537e59.288f6123_boundary
